headline: CME Group Adjusted Interest Rate Total Return Futures Reach Record Open Interest, Volume
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced that its suite of Adjusted Interest Rate (AIR) Total Return futures reached an open interest (OI) record of 710,358 contracts (equivalent to $224 billion notional) on November 20.
